disappearing light<br />
tells you darkness is to come<br />
Ancient rites<br />
the death-mass itself<br />
has never revealed where you will go<br />
You will enter realms where angels fear to tread<br />
open hidden doors within your mind<br />
Sail with Charon sail into destiny<br />
accept your death and make it to your own choice<br />
