<h3><a name="8">8. Mourner's Lament</a></h3><br />
Let me stay here by your side<br />
be one with you my precious child<br />
Let me cover your bed with tears<br />
I will save you from all fears<br />
I burn the candles for your soul<br />
I sing you prayers as the preacher told<br />
I bring you flowers, I dress in black<br />
though I know this cannot give you back<br />
